00:08:57.180 --> 00:08:58.260
<v Nate>So, I don't know.</v>

00:08:58.380 --> 00:08:59.220
<v Nate>It's kind of arbitrary.</v>

00:08:59.420 --> 00:08:59.600
<v Nate>Right.</v>

00:08:59.820 --> 00:09:00.100
